attributes.title: Keep the Change
attributes.caption: While Cameron Campbell struggles to adjust to his new life of community service at camp, Max is determined to prove to David that Campbell is incapable of changing.
attributes.description: While Cameron Campbell struggles to adjust to his new life of community service at camp, Max is determined to prove to David that Campbell is incapable of changing.

attributes.title: Attack of the Nurfs
attributes.caption: The camp gets a 3D printer, but things get out of hand when Nurf decides to print copies of... himself?
attributes.description: The camp gets a 3D printer, but things get out of hand when Nurf decides to print copies of... himself?

attributes.title: Who Peed the Lake?
attributes.caption: During a swim day at the lake, somebody has an accident and it's up to Max to find out who the perpetrator is.
attributes.description: During a swim day at the lake, somebody has an accident and it's up to Max to find out who the perpetrator is.

attributes.title: New Adventure!
attributes.caption: Nikki has a wild series of adventures with an unexpected but supportive pair of campers.
attributes.description: Nikki has a wild series of adventures with an unexpected but supportive pair of campers.

attributes.title: The Quarter-Moon Convergence
attributes.caption: Quartermaster takes the campers out for Astronomy Camp, but clearly has ulterior plans for the night. Neil tries to take the lead and finds himself ill-equipped.
attributes.description: Quartermaster takes the campers out for Astronomy Camp, but clearly has ulterior plans for the night. Neil tries to take the lead and finds himself ill-equipped.

attributes.title: Follow the Leader
attributes.caption: Max, Pikeman, and Sasha are forced to work together to acquire a lost package for Campbell, putting their leadership skills to the test.
attributes.description: Max, Pikeman, and Sasha are forced to work together to acquire a lost package for Campbell, putting their leadership skills to the test.

attributes.title: Preston Goodplay's Good Play
attributes.caption: Preston's new character is a hit with the entire camp, but finds their enthusiasm for more of it overwhelming.
attributes.description: Preston's new character is a hit with the entire camp, but finds their enthusiasm for more of it overwhelming.

attributes.title: After Hours
attributes.caption: The grown-ups deal with a variety of issues around the camp after the campers go to sleep. Mr. Campbell learns to handle some responsibility.
attributes.description: The grown-ups deal with a variety of issues around the camp after the campers go to sleep. Mr. Campbell learns to handle some responsibility.

attributes.title: Camp Loser Says What?
attributes.caption: Camp Campbell falls to the Wood Scouts, whose new leader takes his agenda to extremes they might not be totally comfortable with.
attributes.description: Camp Campbell falls to the Wood Scouts, whose new leader takes his agenda to extremes they might not be totally comfortable with.

attributes.title: Squirrel Camp
attributes.caption: The camp is overrun by vengeful squirrels, displacing the kids and counselors and forcing them to conceive a series of schemes to win the camp back from them.
attributes.description: The camp is overrun by vengeful squirrels, displacing the kids and counselors and forcing them to conceive a series of schemes to win the camp back from them.

attributes.title: Cameron Campbell Can't Handle the Truth Serum
attributes.caption: Campbell accidentally consumes a truth serum just hours before his parole officers are due to check in on his progress. Without the ability to lie, the campers help him find prove his efforts to become a better citizen.
attributes.description: Campbell accidentally consumes a truth serum just hours before his parole officers are due to check in on his progress. Without the ability to lie, the campers help him find prove his efforts to become a better citizen.

attributes.title: The Forest
attributes.caption: David’s survival skills are put to the test when a canoe accident leaves him alone and stranded in the wilderness.
attributes.description: David’s survival skills are put to the test when a canoe accident leaves him alone and stranded in the wilderness.

attributes.title: Campfire Tales
attributes.caption: The camp gathers 'round a campfire and shares some stories of varying spookiness.
attributes.description: The camp gathers 'round a campfire and shares some stories of varying spookiness.

attributes.title: Fashion Victims
attributes.caption: Oh emm gee, did you hear?!?  Don’t tell anyone but Sasha is -like- freaking out over that new girl Ainsley.
attributes.description: Oh emm gee, did you hear?!?  Don’t tell anyone but Sasha is -like- freaking out over that new girl Ainsley. I think it’s cuz Miss Priss picked Ainsley’s idea for the new fundraiser or whatever and now Sasha’s all like scary crazy psycho mad. Anywaaaay, what are you going to wear to the fashion show!?!

attributes.title: Party Pooper
attributes.caption: Gwen's dad unexpectedly drops by camp for a visit, but his presence -- along with everyone idolizing him -- puts strain on Gwen and causes friction between the two. Also, dog.
attributes.description: Gwen's dad unexpectedly drops by camp for a visit, but his presence -- along with everyone idolizing him -- puts strain on Gwen and causes friction between the two. Also, dog.

attributes.title: Panicked Room
attributes.caption: Cameron Campbell finds himself trapped in a makeshift escape room with his most hated rival: Miss Priss! What steamy secrets lie in their shared history? Can they overcome their differences and escape?
attributes.description: Cameron Campbell finds himself trapped in a makeshift escape room with his most hated rival: Miss Priss! What steamy secrets lie in their shared history? Can they overcome their differences and escape?

attributes.title: The Butterfinger Effect
attributes.caption: Space Kid picks up a new hobby and the ripple effect is reaching further than Max is willing to admit. Can Max learn to deal with the aftermath or will he continue to deny the winds of change?
attributes.description: Space Kid picks up a new hobby and the ripple effect is reaching further than Max is willing to admit. Can Max learn to deal with the aftermath or will he continue to deny the winds of change?

attributes.title: Time Crapsules
attributes.caption: Putting together time capsules gets the kids thinking about their futures, but after seeing Gwen not live up to her dreams, it paralyzes them with uncertainty. Meanwhile, Max tries to cheer Gwen up to expedite his transformation into a good person.

attributes.title: St. Campbell's Day - Holiday Special
attributes.caption: Cameron Campbell tries to get a new summertime holiday off the ground with help from the campers, but David suspects he has ulterior motives...

attributes.title: CAMP CAMP: With Friends Like These
attributes.caption: Max, Neil, and Nikki have spent their summer forming friendships. OR HAVE THEY? What if it was all a lie? What if everyone actually hates them? Was any of it real?! Also David discovers social media and it goes exactly as well as you'd expect.
